summary: Completed comprehensive testing of Tamil Nadu service marketplace. Backend APIs working excellently (96.8% success rate), but critical frontend React errors preventing core functionality.

minor_bugs.issue: Returns 404 when trying to remove cart item that was already processed during booking
minor_bugs.impact: Minor - doesn't affect main workflow as bookings auto-clear cart

critical_bugs.issue: Select.Item components have empty string value props causing 'must have a value prop that is not an empty string' error
critical_bugs.selector: All Select components in ServiceDiscovery, ProviderDashboard, etc.
critical_bugs.impact: Service discovery page cannot load, category filters broken

ui_bugs.issue: Entire application has bright yellow background instead of Industrial Pop theme colors
ui_bugs.impact: Poor visual design, text contrast issues, not matching intended Orange/Asphalt theme

integration_issues.issue: JavaScript runtime errors prevent pages with Select components from rendering

passed_tests: Backend: All authentication flows (registration, login, OTP verification)
Backend: Service CRUD operations for providers
Backend: User and provider dashboards data
Frontend: Landing page loads with proper structure
action_item_for_main_agent: CRITICAL: Fix React Select component value prop errors in ServiceDiscovery.js, ProviderDashboard.js and other components using Select. Empty string values need to be replaced with valid values or conditional rendering. Also fix global CSS styling to use proper Industrial Pop theme colors instead of bright yellow background.

success_percentage.frontend: 40% (basic pages load but core functionality broken due to Select component errors)
